        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2011-09-25 14:14:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe \"path2fid\" lfs command prints FIDs within \"[\" and \"]\".  E.g., \"[0x200000400:0x2:0x0]\".",
